 States|Colorado}}\n*[[Philadelphia Toboggan Company Carousel 12]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons}}\n*[http://www.burlingtoncolo.com/ City of Burlington]\n*[http://dtdapps.coloradodot.info/staticdata/Downloads/CityMaps/BURLINGTON.pdf Map of Burlington], CDOT\n*[http://www.bauderhistory.com/pdf/TheEarlyDaysofBurlington.pdf The Early Days of Burlington (PDF)]\n\n{{Kit Carson County, Colorado}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Cities in Kit Carson County, Colorado]]\n[[Category:Cities in Colorado]]\n[[Category:County seats in Colorado]]\n[[Category:German-Russian culture in Colorado]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1887]]\n[[Category:1887 establishments in Colorado]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- Basic info -->\n|name                     = Burlington, Colorado\n|settlement_type          = [[List of cities and towns in Colorado#Home rule municipality|Home Rule Municipality]]\n\n<!-- Images -->\n|image_skyline            = Burlington, Colorado.JPG\n|image_caption            = South Lincoln St. in Burlington\n|image_flag               = \n|image_seal               = <!-- Maps -->\n|image_map                = File:Kit Carson County Colorado Incorporated and Unincorporated areas Burlington Highlighted 0810600.svg\n|map_caption              = Location of Burlington in Kit Carson County, Colorado.\n\n<!-- Location -->\n|coordinates              = {{coord|39.304491|-102.271463|region:US-CO|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|coordinates_footnotes    = <ref name=Gazetteer>{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov/geo/maps-data/data/gazetteer2014.html|title=2014 U.S. Gazetteer Files:  Places|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|date=July 1, 2014|accessdate=January 5, 2015}}</ref>\n|subdivision_type         = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name         = United States\n|subdivision_type1        = [[U.S. state|State]]\n|subdivision_name1        = [[Colorado]]\n|subdivision_type2        = [[